description: This file defines internal API prototypes for the Bbhm Upload Diagnostics Object, including functions for managing upload diagnostics such as engagement, cancellation, setup, teardown, as well as starting, stopping, retrieving results, and configuration management.

methods.name: BbhmUploadCancel
methods.description: Cancels the ongoing upload diagnostic process.

methods.name: BbhmUploadSetupEnv
methods.description: Sets up the environment for upload diagnostics.

methods.name: BbhmUploadCloseEnv
methods.description: Closes and cleans up the upload diagnostic environment.

methods.name: BbhmUploadGetResult
methods.description: Retrieves the result handle of the upload diagnostic.

methods.name: BbhmUploadRetrieveResult
methods.description: Retrieves the upload diagnostic result data.

methods.name: BbhmUploadGetConfig
methods.description: Gets the current configuration of the upload diagnostics.

methods.name: BbhmUploadSetConfig
methods.description: Sets the configuration for upload diagnostics.

methods.name: BbhmUploadSetDiagState
methods.description: Sets the diagnostic state during upload diagnostics.
